%define		_beta	beta1
Version:	1.3
Release:	0.5
License:	GPL v2+
Group:		Applications/Networking
Source0:	http://www.stedee.id.au/files/%{name}-%{version}-%{_beta}.tar.gz
# Source0-md5:	c9843e87412c1bdf8fb2ec5983f0c9c4
